    <title>Introduction</title>

    <sect1>
        <title>Introduction</title>

        <para>Welcome to the Ikasan Enterprise Integration Platform (EIP). There is a already a great deal of material
        written about this platform, but this document will focus on you, the all important end user!</para>

        <para>End users interact with Ikasan via a web browser (supported browsers are listed below) and depending on
        their authentication credentials are allowed to perform a variety of tasks.</para>

        <sect2>
            <title>Supported Browsers</title>

            <para><itemizedlist>
                    <listitem>
                        <para>Firefox 2.0.x/3.0.x/3.5.x</para>
                    </listitem>

                    <listitem>
                        <para>Internet Explorer 7.x/8.x</para>
                    </listitem>

                    <listitem>
                        <para>Google Chrome 2.x/3.x4/x</para>
                    </listitem>

                    <listitem>
                        <para>Safari 4.x</para>
                    </listitem>
                </itemizedlist></para>
        </sect2>

        <sect2>
            <title>Supported Tasks</title>

            <para><itemizedlist>
                    <listitem>
                        <para>Wiretap Event Search</para>
                    </listitem>

                    <listitem>
                        <para>Wiretap Event Details</para>
                    </listitem>
                </itemizedlist></para>
        </sect2>
    </sect1>
